	&quot;The Bear, the Cat and the Rabbit&quot; is a short adventure with couple 
&quot;think outside the box&quot; puzzles. You control three 
anthropomorphic animals on a strange quest in abandoned yet hostile 
environment. All this in semi-isometric, 16-bit 
retro style. 
	<br>
	<br>
	The game itself is a prequel to <a href="http://www.michellagarde.fr/livre/1058/bande-dessinee-l-ours-le-chat-et-le-lapin.html" rel="nofollow">comic book</a> of the same title
